    "body": "## Final verification status\n\n- ✅ \\\"make company-check\\\" → PASS (DEALIX_COMPANY_LAUNCH_READY=1)\n- ✅ \\\"make company-day\\\" → runs end-to-end; verdict NEEDS_SERVER_FIX only because production env vars (APP_SECRET_KEY, DATABASE_URL) are not set in Codespace. Revenue/compliance pipeline is healthy.\n- ✅ \\\"make command-room\\\" → builds reports/command_room/index.html\n- ✅ \\\"make revenue-daily\\\" → generates drafts, proposals, daily report\n- ✅ \\\"make gmail-drafts-dry-run\\\" → dry-run only, no external send\n- ✅ \\\"make server-preflight\\\" → reports missing env vars clearly\n- ✅ git diff --check → clean\n- ✅ pytest -q tests/test_no_auto_external_send.py tests/test_gmail_drafts_only.py → 5 passed\n- ✅ pytest -q tests/test_company_launch_suite.py → 22 passed\n\n### Blocker for full green verdict\nSet production env vars in the target environment:\n- APP_SECRET_KEY\n- DATABASE_URL\n- (optional) REDIS_URL, MOYASAR_SECRET_KEY, HUBSPOT_ACCESS_TOKEN\n- GMAIL_* for Gmail draft creation\n\nThen re-run \\\"make company-day\\\" to get READY_FOR_MANUAL_OUTREACH.",
